You look so frail.

355
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:24,860
Lean on me.

356
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:30,470
You're not my boyfriend,
why should I lean on you?

357
00:28:30,940 --> 00:28:34,890
Whatever, it's not like
you got a boyfriend.

358
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:52,420
