interested in you,

378
00:31:27,330 --> 00:31:29,400
so act properly.

379
00:31:29,470 --> 00:31:31,930
If you're not into her, say
so, but if you do, stick with her.

380
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:34,930
Don't be vague,
and no heartbreaking.

381
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:48,490
