Go.

408
00:33:41,190 --> 00:33:42,800
Holy cow!

409
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,200
Go.

410
00:33:48,970 --> 00:33:50,170
Really?

411
00:33:59,340 --> 00:34:00,340
