419
00:34:52,310 --> 00:34:53,610
Feelings?

420
00:34:53,750 --> 00:34:59,000
When I draw exactly the
same, I get to see my feelings.

421
00:34:59,700 --> 00:35:04,110
I begin to understand
how I feel about this person.

422
00:35:06,180 --> 00:35:09,610
So I have to draw as close
to the real thing as possible.

423
00:35:10,300 --> 00:35:12,770
