that you'll let me leave.</i>

1082
01:46:08,110 --> 01:46:09,110
<i>Ha-eun.</i>

1083
01:46:10,490 --> 01:46:14,280
When the baby is born,
do whatever you want.

1084
01:46:16,200 --> 01:46:19,040
